##       1.551318500      -0.003144654       0.001178540

Comparison

H0: Dispersion patterns
H1: Clustered patterns
\(\alpha=0.05\)

Z-score of contiguity spatial neighbors: \(Z_\mathrm{contiguity}=\frac{0.898830864-(-0.0028089888)}{0.0009842511}\approx710.96303\)

Z-score of K-nearest spatial neightbors: \(Z_\mathrm{knn}=\frac{0.898830864-(-0.002724796)}{0.002181314}\approx413.30852\)

Z-score of distance-based spatial neightbors: \(Z_\mathrm{distance-based}=\frac{1.551318500-(-0.003144654)}{0.001139535}\approx1364.1206\)

比較之下可以看出三種鄰近定義的z-score皆遠大於1.96所以虛無假設(H0)被拒絕。但是\(Z_\mathrm{distance-based}>Z_\mathrm{contiguity}>Z_\mathrm{knn}\)，原因是「鄰近範圍」的不同。Contiguity neightbor只要是共邊/點皆算；K-nearest neighbor只取最近的k個鄰居(在這次實習取k = 2，比起queen’s adjacency還要少)；distance-based neighbor則是在閾值之內皆算。定義的不同也造就了「鄰近密集程度」的不一，所以才會得到三種不同程度的clustered distribution。
